f80c","tid":454701,"uid":115516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>誠哥係唔係話緊比大家知會發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舊公司有個老前輩講過<br />\n<br />\n誠哥最勁係佢背後班人真係一流 好識得計數<br />\n佢話誠哥一買野 3個月至半年後個市就會升<br />\n相反 佢一賣野 之後個市好極都有限</blockquote><br />\n誠哥身邊既CEO，高層成日被抄，換人.....反而四叔 彤叔個d 老臣子好多都做左幾十年，做到退休</blockquote><br />\n  <br />\n你以為啦<br />\n入面一樣勁多權鬥，咪咁天真"},{"pid":"1ee0cca88310ae7235d4686cc5155f709fbcf7ae","tid":454701,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:30:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"547eca7c121ff5966c9d3881ea9057c44b5489ea","tid":454701,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27af3c717159738cf13da210418b5637ec7ae9da","tid":454701,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>長實（1113）出售中環中心大部分樓層權益的交易，最終以作價402億元落實。買家為「中國港澳台僑和平發展亞洲地產有限公司」。</blockquote><br />\n走左好撚耐 好似係<br />\n幾年前己經賣百佳</blockquote><br />\n仲未賣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ded3decd2918d6c47c814436816e9ecc089ae7","tid":454701,"uid":125688,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"中國港澳台僑和平發展亞洲地產, 有冇起底組巴打跟進下?"},{"pid":"ac8c681d44a5ad328e10a9d558be775ba122b137","tid":454701,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國港澳台僑和平發展亞洲地產, 有冇起底組巴打跟進下?</blockquote><br />\n中國港澳台僑和平發展亞洲地產有限公司 C.H.M.T.<br />\nPeaceful Development Asia Property Limited，一間根據英屬處女群島法律註冊成立之公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://iis.quamnet.com/media/IRAnnouncement/1113/ZH_TW/002960898-0.PDF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiis.quamnet.com%2Fmedia%2FIRAnnouncement%2F1113%2FZH_TW%2F002960898-0.PDF&d=%2BfX43UecHCvI3dkyCsNwuQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9d8a389d\" target=\"_blank\">http://iis.quamnet.com/media/IRAnnouncement/1113/ZH_TW/002960898-0.PDF</a>"},{"pid":"ad0c4dad011210187759ceab0a8057d5ad03cfd7","tid":454701,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"過去一年多次傳出易手的中環中心，終於宣布售出！長實(1113)剛公布，其持有的中環中心75%業權，成功以402億元售予中國港澳台僑和平發展亞洲地產有限公司C.H.M.T.Peaceful Development Asia Property Limited，為一家海外註冊公司，物業成交呎價約3.3萬元。<br />\n<br />\n對於中環中心的交易，長實發言人回應稱：「買賣房地產是公司的本業，我們的日常業務，政府都是一幅幅土地出售。很多香港公司的物業都是出售予支那企業，今時今日這是很普通的事，沒有賣家，國際及支那新資金怎有渠道來香港?」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171101/s00003/1509537332734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171101%2Fs00003%2F1509537332734&d=%2BfX43UecHCvI3dkyCsNwuQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ca85fe26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171101%2Fs00003%2F1509537332734&h=ef55f7a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171101/s00003/1509537332734</a>"},{"pid":"b08b7877c482bb970405540a4c017b9af53d64ad","tid":454701,"uid":27664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"乜都係中國公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5b9678fe2a9be3ff103224b65ebd737305c773","tid":454701,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"通告並無介紹買方的背景，只表示為一家在英屬處女群島註冊成立的公司。早前有傳買家為中資機構，但由於今次披露的買家是專為收購成立的BVI公司，令外界難以追查其背景。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>《蘋果日報》則引市場消息指，買家為一個組合，包括中國國儲能淡化工集團(香港) 及多名本地投資者包括小巴大王馬亞木、磁帶大王陳秉志、亞洲地產蔡志忠及「物流張」張順宜。其中國儲佔大股55%，其餘45%則由其他投資者攤分。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E9%95%B7%E5%AF%A6402%E5%84%84%E6%B2%BD%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E